edu.ncsu.csc216.tracker.ticket_tracker

Class TicketTrackerModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.tracker.ticket_tracker.TicketTrackerModel

  • public class TicketTrackerModel
extends java.lang.Object
    TicketTrackerModel maintains the current TrackedTicketList and handles activity around loading, saving, and creating new TrackedTicketLists. For this, TicketTrackerModel will use TicketReader and TicketWriter from the TicketXML library.
    Author:
    Scott Spencer
